# Production Database & Backend Implementation Plan

The objective is to transition the OICA educational portal from a simulation-based `localStorage` architecture to a robust production environment with a centralized database and backend.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Choice**: We are proceeding with a **Node.js/Express** backend and a **PostgreSQL** database as requested. We will use **Prisma ORM** for type-safe database access.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Migration**: Existing `localStorage` data will be discarded. We will start with a fresh PostgreSQL schema and seed it with premium demo data.

## Proposed Database Schema

### 1. `branches`
Stores information about physical OICA centers.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `branch_code`: `VARCHAR(20)` (Unique, e.g., 'KHORDHA-01')
- `name`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `location`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `manager_name`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `phone`: `VARCHAR(20)`
- `email`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `address`: `TEXT`
- `about_text`: `TEXT`
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 2. `users`
Centralized user table for Students, Admins, and Branch Managers.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `branch_id`: `UUID` (FK to `branches.id`, Nullable for HQ Admins)
- `name`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `email`: `VARCHAR(100)` (Unique)
- `username`: `VARCHAR(50)` (Unique)
- `password_hash`: `TEXT`
- `role`: `ENUM('admin', 'branch', 'student')`
- `roll_no`: `VARCHAR(50)` (Unique, Nullable)
- `course_id`: `UUID` (FK to `courses.id`, Nullable)
- `photo_url`: `TEXT`
- `phone`: `VARCHAR(20)`
- `age`: `INTEGER`
- `completed_video_ids`: `JSONB` (Array of Lecture IDs)
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 3. `notices`
Campus broadcasts and announcements.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `branch_id`: `UUID` (FK to `branches.id`)
- `title`: `VARCHAR(255)`
- `link_url`: `TEXT` (Optional)
- `posted_date`: `DATE`
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 4. `courses` (Topics)
Academic modules.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `name`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `category`: `VARCHAR(50)` (e.g., 'PGDCA', 'DCA')
- `sort_order`: `INTEGER`
- `description`: `TEXT`
- `ui_color`: `VARCHAR(20)` (e.g., 'blue', 'emerald')
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 5. `lectures`
Video content within courses.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `course_id`: `UUID` (FK to `courses.id`)
- `title`: `VARCHAR(255)`
- `description`: `TEXT`
- `video_url`: `TEXT`
- `thumbnail_url`: `TEXT`
- `duration`: `VARCHAR(20)`
- `sort_order`: `INTEGER`
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 6. `mock_tests`
Assessments for courses.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `course_id`: `UUID` (FK to `courses.id`, or NULL for general)
- `is_final`: `BOOLEAN`
- `time_limit_mins`: `INTEGER`
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 7. `questions`
Individual test questions.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `test_id`: `UUID` (FK to `mock_tests.id`)
- `question_text`: `TEXT`
- `options`: `JSONB` (Array of strings)
- `correct_index`: `INTEGER`
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 8. `test_results`
Student performance tracking.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `student_id`: `UUID` (FK to `users.id`)
- `test_id`: `UUID` (FK to `mock_tests.id`)
- `score`: `INTEGER`
- `total_questions`: `INTEGER`
- `taken_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 9. `attendance`
Daily presence logs.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `student_id`: `UUID` (FK to `users.id`)
- `branch_id`: `UUID` (FK to `branches.id`)
- `log_date`: `DATE`
- `log_time`: `TIME`
- `marked_by`: `VARCHAR(50)` (e.g., 'system', 'branch_manager')
- `method`: `VARCHAR(20)` (e.g., 'barcode', 'manual')
- `status`: `VARCHAR(20)` (e.g., 'present', 'absent')

### 10. `jobs` & `job_applications`
Career portal data.
- **Jobs**: `title`, `company`, `location`, `salary`, `requirements`, `posted_at`
- **Applications**: `job_id`, `student_id`, `status` ('Pending', 'Shortlisted'), `applied_at`

### 11. `inquiries`
Unified table for all leads (Contact, Franchise, Admissions).
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `type`: `ENUM('contact', 'franchise', 'admission')`
- `name`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `email`: `VARCHAR(100)`
- `phone`: `VARCHAR(20)`
- `message`: `TEXT`
- `status`: `VARCHAR(20)` ('New', 'Contacted', 'Resolved')
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

### 12. `feedback`
Student testimonials.
- `id`: `UUID` (PK)
- `student_id`: `UUID` (FK to `users.id`)
- `rating`: `INTEGER` (1-5)
- `comment`: `TEXT`
- `is_approved`: `BOOLEAN` (Default: false)
- `created_at`: `TIMESTAMP`

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] [NEW]
- **Environment**: Node.js with Express.js.
- **ORM**: Prisma for PostgreSQL.
- **Location**: All backend code will reside in a new `/server` directory.
- **Authentication**: JWT-based authentication for students, branch managers, and admins.
- **Endpoints**:
  - `/api/auth`: Login and session management.
  - `/api/student`: Dashboard data, video progress, test results.
  - `/api/branch`: Student management, notice board, branch profile.
  - `/api/admin`: Branch management, inbox/leads, analytics.
- **Demo Data**: A dedicated `seed.ts` script to populate all tables with 200+ demo records.

### [Frontend]
- Replace `src/lib/storage.ts` logic with API calls (using `axios` or Supabase client).
- Update components to fetch data from the production database.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Verify CRUD operations for all tables via Postman/Thunder Client.
- Test authentication flows for all 3 roles.

### Manual Verification
- Login as Student, Branch Manager, and Admin to ensure data isolation.
- Post a notice as Branch Manager and verify it appears on the Student Dashboard.
- Submit an admission inquiry and verify it appears in the Admin Inbox.
